items.description: Oh my dear Cindy! What a beautiful gift you gave me. üôè At the very moment I am sitting speechless on a bench in the city Forbes, in NSW. And..... that was gone yesterday! üí• Yep,  the cause were earfuckers, for sure! And yep, by kicking those assholes out, silence/stillness came. And trust, hope, love and a lot more!! (I promised Emily not to use ChatGPT anymore to 'write' my messages! üòÅ) Also she said yesterday, independently from you, that I did the work! Can you imagine!???
